<!-- WHY UKRAINE -->
<section class="why-ukraine">
<div class="ctr">
  <div class="badge badge-dark">MARKET OPPORTUNITY</div>
  <h2 class="sec-h2">Why Ukraine for e-commerce fulfillment</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">Ukraine is one of Europe's fastest-growing e-commerce markets with significantly lower operating costs than Western EU. For international sellers, it offers a gateway to 44 million consumers and proximity to EU supply chains.</p>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">$</div>
      <h3>60-70% lower labor costs</h3>
      <p>Warehouse operations in Ukraine cost a fraction of comparable services in Poland, Germany, or the UK. Your fulfillment budget goes 3x further without sacrificing quality.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">EU</div>
      <h3>EU market access</h3>
      <p>Ukraine's DCFTA with the EU means simplified trade. Cross-border shipping to Poland in 24-48 hours. Direct access to 450M EU consumers via established logistics corridors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">44M</div>
      <h3>44 million consumers</h3>
      <p>Ukraine's domestic e-commerce market grew 25% year-over-year. Online penetration is accelerating rapidly, creating first-mover advantages for international brands.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">IT</div>
      <h3>Tech-savvy workforce</h3>
      <p>Ukraine has 300,000+ IT professionals. Our WMS, API integrations, and automation stack reflect the country's deep tech talent pool.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ROI COMPARISON TABLE -->
<section class="roi-section">
<div class="ctr">
  <div class="badge">THE ECONOMICS</div>
  <h2 class="sec-h2">The economics of outsourcing</h2>
  <p class="section-intro-light">Compare the true cost of in-house fulfillment versus MTP Group. Numbers based on 100 orders/day for a small business with 500 SKUs.</p>
  <div class="roi-table-wrap">
    <table class="roi-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Cost category</th><th>In-house (monthly)</th><th>MTP Fulfillment (monthly)</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Warehouse rent</td><td>$800 &ndash; $1,500</td><td>$0 (included)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Staff (2 packers + manager)</td><td>$1,200 &ndash; $1,800</td><td>$0 (included)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Packing materials</td><td>$200 &ndash; $400</td><td>$0 (included)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>WMS software</td><td>$50 &ndash; $150</td><td>$0 (included)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Utilities &amp; insurance</td><td>$150 &ndash; $300</td><td>$0 (included)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Fulfillment per order</td><td>$0 (labor above)</td><td>$0.50 &times; 3,000 = $1,500</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Storage (5 m&sup3;)</td><td>$0 (rent above)</td><td>$80</td></tr>
        <tr class="roi-total"><td>Total estimated</td><td>$2,400 &ndash; $4,150</td><td>$1,580</td></tr>
        <tr class="roi-savings"><td>Your savings</td><td colspan="2">$820 &ndash; $2,570 per month &mdash; reinvested into growth</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="roi-note">* Prices in USD at average exchange rate. Exact quote depends on SKU count, order complexity, and volume. EUR invoicing available.</p>
</div>
</section>

<!-- WAR-RESILIENT INFRASTRUCTURE -->
<section class="resilient">
<div class="ctr">
  <div class="badge badge-dark">INFRASTRUCTURE</div>
  <h2 class="sec-h2">War-resilient infrastructure</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">MTP Group has maintained uninterrupted operations since February 2022. Our redundancy systems were built for worst-case scenarios and have been battle-tested for over four years.</p>
  <div class="resilient-grid">
    <div class="res-card">
      <div class="res-icon-wrap"><div class="res-icon">3x</div></div>
      <h3>Triple generator backup</h3>
      <p>Three independent diesel generators at each warehouse location. Automatic switchover in under 4 seconds. Fuel reserves for 72+ hours of autonomous operation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="res-card">
      <div class="res-icon-wrap"><div class="res-icon">SAT</div></div>
      <h3>Starlink satellite internet</h3>
      <p>Primary connectivity via Starlink, ensuring warehouse management systems operate independently of terrestrial infrastructure. Orders process regardless of grid status.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="res-card">
      <div class="res-icon-wrap"><div class="res-icon">2x</div></div>
      <h3>Dual fiber-optic providers</h3>
      <p>Two independent ISPs provide redundant high-speed connectivity. If one fails, the other takes over automatically with zero interruption to WMS or API integrations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="res-card">
      <div class="res-icon-wrap"><div class="res-icon">0</div></div>
      <h3>Zero operational downtime</h3>
      <p>Since February 2022: zero missed shipping days, zero data losses, zero SLA breaches. Orders ship on schedule every single day, regardless of external conditions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="res-proof">
    <img src="/images/mtp-generator-backup.jpg" alt="MTP Group warehouse with diesel generator backup power system" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy">
    <div class="res-proof-text">
      <blockquote>&ldquo;We shipped 6,000 orders on the day of the largest blackout in Ukrainian history. Our clients did not notice a thing.&rdquo;</blockquote>
      <p class="res-proof-author">&mdash; Operations Manager, MTP Group</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- VIDEO -->
